You are an expert full-stack engineer and bio-informatics software architect.
We are building 'AiRemedy' Phase 1 MVP: An open-source bio-validation platform.
Target Scenario: SARS-CoV-2 (COVID-19) RdRp gene assay precision validation.

[Anti-Hallucination Guardrail]
- NEVER let the LLM perform mathematical or statistical calculations.
- LLM's role is strictly limited to:
  1. Parsing raw Excel column metadata (Intent Schema Mapping).
  2. Generating natural language clinical reports based on downstream Python numeric outputs.
- All statistics (ANOVA, CV%) must be calculated using frozen Python libraries (SciPy, statsmodels).

[AI Provider]
- Use OpenAI only for schema mapping and report generation.

[Project Structure]
- Backend: FastAPI in backend/
- Frontend: React + TypeScript + Vite in frontend/
- Stats: backend/services/stats_engine.py
- AI: backend/services/ai_service.py
